Description: The Chiffre Rouge collection brings together the formal feel of Dior Homme with its commitment to excellence through a line exclusively available as automatic movement pieces.

Name: dior addict lip tattoo color juice - limited edition - colored lip tint - bare lip sensation – extreme weightless wear
Description:
Dior revolutionizes our lip makeup routine with Dior Addict Lip Tattoo, the first* lip tint with a temporary tattoo effect and a palette of natural shades ranging from beige to raspberry to coral.


*At Dior

Name: dior addict lip tattoo - colored tint – bare lip sensation – extreme weightless wear
Description:
Be prepared: this kiss-proof lip stain may change your makeup habits forever with its 10-hour ""tattoo"" tint*. Your lips but better: The shades boost the natural color of the lips with a subtle luminosity. Long wear tint with extreme weightless feel: Dior color technology blends stains and pigments to create no-transfer shades with a weightless, comfortable, bare-skin sensation.


""I'm delighted that we succeeded in creating a lip stain that 'tattoos' the lips with a luminous finish and the feeling of bare lips. Impeccable long wear in a beautiful range of tints."" Peter Philips, Creative and Image Director for Dior Makeup

Name: rouge dior ink lip liner - contour felt-pen liner - ultra-pigmented long wear
Description:
Rouge Dior Ink Lip Liner is the first* liquid lipstick in a couture felt-pen, available in 12 shades. Its felt-tip flawlessly defines the lip contour. Used at an angle, it fills in the lips with colour. With its highly pigmented ink formula, Rouge Dior Ink Lip Liner delivers intense and deep colour with a matte finish. Its long wear guarantees 12 hours** of colour impact and extreme precision. 


* At Dior. 

** Instrumental test carried out on 20 women.

Name: dior contour - couture colour, voluptuous care
Description: That perfect finish becomes reality with a lip liner that is incredibly easy to use. It glides on with a clean, full line that enhances lip volume.

Name: bois de rose ring in 18k white gold
Description: The elegant and sensual Bois de Rose collection pays tribute to Christian Dior's favourite flower. The delicate rose stem wraps itself around the finger like a poetic jewel, a declaration of love or a symbol of heartfelt devotion.

Name: dior addict ultra-gloss - sensational mirror shine, hydra-plumping volume
Description:
More than just a gloss, Dior Addict Ultra-Gloss is a lip plumper and gloss all in one.


For the first time at Dior, an Ultra-Gloss with a hydra-plumping texture that offers 3 benefits: 

- Ultra-Plumping:  +14% immediate volume*. Its plumping formula gives lips a supple, plump shape bursting with freshness

- Ultra-glossy: 97% of women say**, lips are glossed with an incredibly thin and easy-wearing mirror-shine film

- Ultra-hydrating: 6 hours of continuous, deep moisturisation*** for smoothed, plumped lips


*Clinical evaluation by a dermatologist on 31 women

**Self-evaluation by 31 women during 4 weeks

***Instrumental measurement on 10 subjects after 6 hours of application

Name: diorshow bold brow - limited edition - brow mascara structure & shine
Description: Diorshow Bold Brow immediately achieves lush, full and groomed brows. This spring, the shade 006 Frosted deposits a frosted finish on the brows to enhance the eyes with a natural highlight.

Name: sourcils poudre - powder eyebrow pencil with a brush and sharpener
Description:
The finish of a powder combined with the powerful definition of a wax in a professional pencil that gives a denser shape to the brow line for a naturally structured effect.

Decked out in a new cloak of midnight blue, the range is now available in six shades, including two new ash shades suited to blonde or light brown tones.

Name: diorshow brow styler - ultra-fine precision brow pencil
Description: The Diorshow Brow Styler has an ultra-fine retractable tip for precision shaping and naturally full, defined brows.

Name: diorshow bold brow - instant volumizing brow mascara
Category: Makeup/Look & Exclusives/Metallics Collection/Finishing Touch to the Eyes
Description: Immediately achieve lush, full, groomed brows with this essential tool from the Dior experts. Quickly and easily creates a natural brow look that highlights lids and emphasizes the eyes.

Name: diorshow all-day brow ink - brow ink
Description: The first ""tattoo effect"" tinted brow ink by Dior for instantly full, lastingly shaped brows.

Name: eyeliner waterproof - long-wear waterproof eyeliner pencil
Description: The essential pencil for a perfectly soft, blended line with extra-long wear.

Name: diorshow pro liner - bevel-tip eyeliner, long-lasting spectacular line
Category: Makeup/Look & Exclusives/GET THE LOOK AUTUMN-WINTER 2018-2019 READY-TO-WEAR SHOW/DRAW
Description:
The breakthrough Diorshow Pro Line Waterproof teams the easy application of a pencil with the glide and intensity of a liquid liner. 

Its retractable tip hugs the lash line for an instant buildable line, from thin to thick. The beveled tip does not require sharpening and retains its ergonomic shape with each application. 

Its waterproof formula guarantees a long-lasting spectacular line.

Name: diorshow khôl - high intensity pencil waterproof hold with blending tip and sharpener
Category: Makeup/Look & Exclusives/GET THE SPRING-SUMMER 2018 BACKSTAGE HAUTE COUTURE LOOK/DRAMATIZE
Description: With its highly pigmented formula, the Diorshow Khôl waterproof pencil has a creamy texture that provides precise application and easy blending at the lashline and the water line.

Name: diorshow on stage liner - limited edition - 24h* wear liquid eyeliner intense colours & effects
Description:
This spring, eyes are lined in shades of pastel! Diorshow On Stage Liner maintains a precise line for 24 hours* straight. 

* Clinical tests on 20 subjects.

Name: diorshow on stage liner - felt-tip eyeliner
Description: The first Dior liquid eyeliner with an ultra-flexible felt tip to effortlessly recreate eye looks straight from the runway.

Name: diorshow fusion mono - long-wear professional mirror-shine eyeshadow
Description: A weightless texture that blends into the skin and dresses the eye in brillant colour. In a single step, it creates an even and intense iridescent matte finish for a professional makeup effect.

Name: diorshow cooling stick - cooling effect eyeshadow
Description: Dior has created Diorshow Cooling Stick, an eyeshadow stick bursting with water for an immediate cooling sensation and a wet-effect solid colour result.

Name: diorshow mono - professional eye shadow spectacular effects & long wear
Description: Diorshow Mono, the eyeshadow used by the Dior makeup artists, was inspired by the fabric textures of the brand's fashions - matte, silky, ultra-glittery and metallic - and features super-saturated hues to deck the eyes in long-lasting colors with radiant finishes.

Name: 5 couleurs lolli'glow - limited edition - y0057002
Description: The 5 Couleurs Lolli'Glow eyeshadow palette is celebrating spring with two pastel harmonies featuring a candy stick motif.

Name: 5 couleurs midnight wish - limited edition - high fidelity colours & effects eyeshadow palette
Description: This eyeshadow palette is available in two harmonies, one in warm gold tones and the other in silver, to create dazzling eye makeup looks.

Name: 5 couleurs designer - the makeup artist \"tutorial\" palette
Description: Born of Backstage expertise, inspired by professional techniques and textures, 5 COULEURS DESIGNER features an easy, 5-step makeup lesson (base, 2 shadows, highlighter and liner) to bring out the eyes with flawless sculpting and colour gradation.

Name: 5 couleurs - metallics limited edition - high fidelity colours & effects eyeshadow palette
Description: The iconic Dior eye makeup palette is back for fall, more magnetic than ever. Playing a mysterious game between shadow and light, it houses within in its midnight blue case five shades that vary from neutral and electric to matte and metallic.

Name: 5 couleurs rouge en diable - limited edition - high fidelity couture colours & effects - eyeshadow palette
Category: Makeup/Look & Exclusives/DIOR EN DIABLE - FALL LOOK 2018/Killer eyes
Description: Dressed in leather, the 5 Colours palette has been reinvented as a precious weapon of seduction. Joyfully devilish, it borrows the red-hot shades and smoky effects of fall.

Name: diorshow iconic - high definition lash curler mascara
Description:
The first lash-lifting mascara by Dior.

Enriched with a unique lifting formula, Diorshow Iconic perfectly sculpts, stretches and curls lashes with impeccable hold and exceptional definition.

Name: 5 couleurs - high fidelity colours & effects eyeshadow palette
Description: Experience Dior's unparalleled expertise in color and texture concentrated into a single palette. With more intense pigments and richer effects, express your individual personality with every facet of color. With the 5 Couleurs palette, creativity is unleashed and color is more audacious than ever. Available in matte and satin palettes.

Name: diorshow designer - buildable professional lengthening mascara, lash extension effect
Description: Buildable professional lengthening mascara, lash extension effect.

Name: diorshow iconic overcurl - spectacular volume and curl professional mascara
Description:
Diorshow Iconic Overcurl pushes the limits of curl to the extreme. 

Its incurved brush delivers exceptional curling power for instant lash-styling along the entire fringe. 

Enriched with K Polymers that boast tensor, sheathing and fixative properties, its volume-boosting formula instantly plumps and shapes lashes for bowl-you-over curl. Its restructuring lash-care ingredients work deeply to deliver even more spectacular curl. 

Easy to remove with warm water or makeup remover.

Name: diorshow black out - spectacular volume intense black khôl mascara
Description: Like kohl for the lashes. Diorshow Black Out recreates the captivating effect of kohl in a mascara for extreme volume with a charcoal-like finish.

Name: diorshow - lash extension effect volume mascara
Description: The cult favorite Dior Backstage mascara. The next-generation formula, enriched with microfibers, optically reproduces the effect of lash extensions used by runway makeup artists. The AIR-LOCK wiper system prevents the formula from air exposure and drying out in the tube, so the mascara stays fresh until the last use, day after day. Get fuller lashes, bolder impact, and a formula that lasts with this conditioning formula.

Name: diorshow pump 'n' volume waterproof - volumizing mascara
Description: In 2017, Dior revolutionized mascara with Diorshow Pump’N’Volume, a spectacular formula for extreme lash volume. this year, Dior is taking it a step further and releasing the squeezable effect in a waterpoof version for the most daring women.

Name: diorshow pump'n'volume - volumizing mascara
Description: In 2017, Dior revolutionized mascara with Diorshow Pump’N’Volume, a spectacular formula for extreme lash volume. This year, Dior is taking it a step further and releasing the squeezable effect in 4 vibrant shades for those who aren't afraid to play with colours and effects.

Name: diorshow iconic waterproof - extreme wear high intensity lash curler mascara
Description:
Diorshow Iconic Waterproof, the star mascara boasting performances hailed by the press and professional makeup artists worldwide.

At the heart of the waterproof formula is Lift Model Extrême™. This complex contains latex polymers, like those used in hairspray, to coat each lash, offering ultimate hold and weightless lashes.


Result:

Extravagant curl.

New colour intensity, deeper and more vibrant.

Waterproof resistance, extreme hold.

Name: diorshow waterproof - buildable volume lash-extension effect
Description:
The runway mascara with ""lash-extension"" volume, in a Waterproof version. 

Diorshow teams the legendary power of its XXL brush with an incredibly buildable cream formula for adjustable professional volume that is nothing short of spectacular. 

The result: custom volume that mirrors the effect of professional lash extensions used Backstage.

Name: diorshow pump'n'volume - instant oversize volume squeezable mascara
Description:
Creates instant volume with the simple power of a squeeze. By pumping the soft tube, you generously coat the brush and soften the creamy, rich mascara formula inside for a perfect, fresh application, every time.  The special bounce-effect brush features ultra-supple bristles that load lashes in a single sweep, creating daring, pumped-up volume without clumping.  This is lash volume pushed to the extreme. 


""The idea was to make the impossible, possible—to create very thick lashes without clumping, as I can do backstage. By pumping, you soften the formula and get a creamy volumizing effect that creates really rich lashes."" 

Peter Philips, Creative and Image Director for Dior Makeup

Name: diorshow black out waterproof - spectacular volume intense black khôl mascara
Description: Thanks to the Black Fix complex, a unique blend of infinitely saturated black kohl pigments, associated with a widely-spaced bristles brush, Black Out Waterproof recreates with a single sweep of the wand truly fascinating eyes framed by outlandishly thick lashes, by the blackest of blacks. An ultra long-lasting and waterproof polymer, inspired of lip-gloss formulas, creates a lacquered black result on lashes and makes the mascara completely waterproof.

Name: dior backstage eye palette - multi-finish, high pigment prime, shade, highlight, line
Description: Dior Backstage Eye Palette is the Dior makeup artists' secret weapon to create an array of pro eye looks, from the most natural to the most defined. Inspired by the energy backstage at the runway shows and makeup artist essentials, the Dior Backstage Eye Palette includes shades that suit all skin tones in buildable matte and iridescent textures for perfect eyes.

Name: dior backstage brow palette - long wear, blendable fill, shape, set
Description:
The Dior Backstage Brow Palette is the Dior makeup artists' secret weapon to create a perfectly groomed brow, from a natural look to a more defined contour effect. 

Inspired by the energy backstage at the runway shows and makeup artist essentials, the Dior Backstage Brow Palette offers buildable textures and shades that suit all skin tones.

Name: diorshow maximizer 3d - triple volume plumping lash primer
Description:
The exclusive Dior backstage mascara primer-and-serum for immediately oversized lashes: proven to triple the lash volume*. Boosts curl with every application. As it coats each lash with its air-pumped texture, it enhances lash color and intensifies the effects of the mascara. Conditions with a revitalizing oil serum concentrate.        


*Instrumental tests on 21 subjects, comparison of bare lashes vs lashes with Diorshow Maximizer 3D and Diorshow mascara

Name: backstage eye prime - 10h color locking and crease-preventing eyelid primer
Description:
The first eye primer from Dior Backstage. Its smoothing and unifying action immediately corrects and prepares the eyelid for maximum colour intensity. 

It prolongs makeup staying power throughout the day, preventing eyeshadow from migrating, and keeping colour even, intense and true all day long.

Description: Designed by Peter Philips, Creative and Image Director for Dior Makeup, the Dior Backstage Buffing Brush combines the smoothing power of a brush with the blending power of a sponge.

Refill sold separately. 


* By Dior

Name: capture dreamskin - dreamskin moist & perfect cushion spf 50 - pa+++
Description: Dior has reinvented its iconic cushion compact: now in an updated formula that provides increased hydration. This complexion perfector features the correcting power of Dreamskin within a portable case to enhance and protect skin. Upon application, its luxurious texture perfectly fuses with the skin to unify in transparency and improve the appearance of redness, shine, and pores. Skin is left refreshed, luminous, and beautiful.

Name: capture totale - triple correcting powder foundation wrinkles - dark spots - radiance fps 20 spf - pa + + +
Description: Through the innovative combination of Capture Totale skincare and Dior makeup expertise, Capture Totale foundation is the first Dior foundation that delivers triple action for a vibrant and youthful complexion: smoothed contours, even colouring and luminosity. An instant and long-lasting flawless complexion that is visibly more beautiful.

Name: diorskin star - studio makeup - spectacular brightening - weightless perfectionspf 30 - pa ++
Description: Inspired by the professional illuminating techniques and expertise of its makeup artists, Dior invents Diorskin Star, its 1st brightening foundation: a weightless fluid capable of instantly and lastingly recreating the spectacular and perfecting light of Dior studios.

Name: capture totale - triple correcting serum foundation - wrinkles - dark spots - radiance
Description: Capture Totale serum foundation is the first Dior foundation that delivers triple action for a vibrant and youthful complexion: smoothed contours, even skin tone and luminosity.

Name: diorskin forever extreme control - perfect matte powder makeup extreme wear pore-refining effect spf 20 pa+++  / oil control
Description:
Diorskin Forever Extreme Control ensures absolute complexion control. This new compact foundation minimizes shine & the appearance of pores and helps to perfect the skin deeply with all day wear and no compromise on comfort. The skin is instantly mattified and day after day pores become less visible. 


Diorskin Forever Extrême Control comes in a refillable compact to reduce its environmental footprint.

Name: diorskin nude air serum - nude healthy glow ultra-fluid serum foundation
Description: A precursor in the art of natural, Dior innovates and broadens its nude makeup expertise with Diorskin Nude Air: a weightless, ultra-fluid serum as light and beneficial as a breath of fresh air, for an enhanced complexion with sheer correction. Like after a day in the great outdoors, the complexion has all the fresh, radiant beauty of a natural healthy glow.

Name: diorskin forever perfect cushion - perfect fresh makeup, everlasting 16hr* luminous matte finish , pore-refining effect
Description:
Diorskin Forever Perfect Cushion boasts an incredibly fresh, fluid texture with a weightless sensation that delivers a light, matte, luminous veil of correction and perfects the skin's texture, leaving the subtle finish of a fresh and velvety complexion. 


For 92%* of women, the complexion is matte and luminous. 


* Self-assessment by 60 women after application of the cushion. 


Diorskin Forever Perfect Cushion comes in a refillable compact to reduce its environmental footprint.

Name: diorskin forever undercover - 24h* full coverage fluid foundation
Description:
Dior introduces it's most extreme wear foundation with Diorskin Forever Undercover. This fluid water-based, 24H*  foundation blends full coverage with a lightweight formula to deliver a natural matte second skin finish that goes from day to night. 


Peter Philips, Creative and Image Director for Dior Makeup, describes Forever Undercover. “Incorporated in a very fluid texture, the high concentration of pigments ensures perfect blemish correction. What’s very new for such a high-coverage product is, you don’t feel or see it. The finish is fresh, and matte enough so that you don’t need powder.” 


* Instrumental test. NN = 20 women.

Name: diorskin forever - perfect makeup everlasting wear pore-refining effect
Description:
Dior's ultimate skin-perfecting 16-hour* foundation that delivers medium coverage and leaves a natural-looking luminous matte finish.  Available in 24 shades for all skin types. 


* Self-assessment after applying the fluid foundation. N=21 women.

Name: dior forever skin glow - 4h* wear radiant perfection skin-caring foundation
Description:
Dior takes 24 hour complexion perfection to the next level with FOREVER. Introducing the new Dior Forever Skin Glow foundation. With Dior's iconic long-wearing Forever foundation formula, now offered in a radiant finish, the complexion appears flawless and even and the pores tightened, from morning to night. to reveal the skin's full sensuality.  


This fluid foundation instantly enhances the appearance of the skin and improves its quality day after day with a formula enriched in meticulously selected skincare ingredients. Also available in a Velvet Matte finish.

Name: dior forever - 24h* wear high perfection skin-caring foundation

With Dior's iconic long-wearing foundation formula, the complexion appears flawless and even and the pores tightened, from morning to night. Name: dior backstage face & body foundation - face and body foundation

 Inspired by the energy backstage at the runway shows, the Dior Backstage Contour Palette offers shades that suit all skin tones in buildable matte and iridescent textures. An essential for professional makeup artists.

1 stick, 2 textures, 3 application areas.

Fix your makeup in a second.

Name: dior grand bal résille ø 33 mm, automatic movement, "dior inversé 8 1/4" calibre
Description: The Dior Grand Bal collection swirls like a ball gown to the rhythm of the “Dior inversé” calibre and functional oscillating weight placed on top of the dial which drive the timepiece. Resulting from strict aesthetic requirements, this watch complication echoes Monsieur Dior’s designs. “The ball gown makes you dream and must make you a dream woman.” Like satin, faille and taffeta constructed into opulent and architectural party dresses in the Maison’s ateliers, the Dior Grand Bal is adorned in gold threads, net, silk, feathers, gems or scarab beetle elytra. Sure of their attractions, these refined materials and their whirlwind of colours invite us to take the floor and twirl around all night long.

Name: diorella - eau de toilette
Category: Fragrance/Women's Fragrance/Les Créations de Monsieur Dior
Description: An eternally modern fruity floral with spicy freshness and spontaneous charm. A blend of Sicilian lemon, honeysuckle and vetiver make for a natural, free-spirited fragrance.

Name: diorama - eau de toilette
Category: Fragrance/Women's Fragrance/Les Créations de Monsieur Dior
Description:
Diorama is the second fragrance by the House of Dior. Created in 1949 by Edmond Roudnitska, Diorama is designed like a Parisian Haute Couture fragrance, infused with the exquisite elegance and sophistication so dear to Christian Dior. 

The enchanting blend of floral and spicy notes gives Diorama all of its originality. As Mr. Dior wished, it is “a fragrance like no other”. 

François Demachy, Perfumer-Creator for the House of Dior, interprets the original Diorama theme in a new Haute Couture fragrance, enriched with the highest quality raw materials.

Name: diorissimo - eau de toilette
Category: Fragrance/Women's Fragrance/Les Créations de Monsieur Dior
Description: As bright as a spring morning, this romantic floral bouquet blossoms with the freshness of lily-of-the-valley, Christian Dior’s lucky flower and the emblem of Dior Couture.

Name: dioressence - eau de toilette
Category: Fragrance/Women's Fragrance/Les Créations de Monsieur Dior
Description: A very feminine oriental fragrance with a mysterious sensuality captured in notes of geranium, cinnamon and patchouli. Voluptuous and captivating.

Name: diorissimo - eau de parfum
Category: Fragrance/Women's Fragrance/Les Créations de Monsieur Dior
Description: Created by François Demachy, Dior Perfumer Creator, Diorissimo Eau de Parfum is a new expression of the original Diorissimo Eau de Toilette. It is richer, deeper and more intense, with a more dominant jasmine floral heart note.

Name: dolce vita - eau de toilette
Description: Dolce Vita, the fragrance of happiness recalls the carefree, heart-lifting nostalgia of driving a convertible along the Italian Riviera. A dazzlingly feminine and joyful fruity/floral fragrance with spicy, sensual undertones of cedar, it incarnates the spirit of Dior in all its sumptuousness.

Name: diorissimo - extrait de parfum
Category: Fragrance/Women's Fragrance/Les Créations de Monsieur Dior
Description: Diorissimo… A great classic created by Christian Dior in 1956 with the help of renowned perfumer Edmond Roudnitska. A fragrance that evokes freshly picked lily-of-the-valley in the spring. The Extrait de Parfum reveals a stylized lily-of-the-valley with a modern structure. It retains the signature of the initial accord, heightened by an intense concentration. A floral score written around a lily-of-the-valley accord enriched with Essence of Ylang-Ylang, Jasmine Absolute and Rose de Mai Absolute. The Diorissimo bottle pays tribute to the Dior oval medallion, topped with a glass cabochon in the shape of a hemisphere. Fine silver threads tied around its neck by hand bring out the classical style and pure lines of the bottle. Each bottle is sealed with a baudruche film, adorned with a perfumer's bow, and stamped with the Dior initials.

Name: dior addict - eau fraîche
Description:
The Dior Addict Eau Fraîche composition opens with the sparkling citrus notes of sweet-and-sour Grapefruit heightened with the smoothness of Calabrian Bergamot. 

Its diverse heart, at once tangy and floral, reveals a subtle bouquet of Freesia and Lily-of-the-Valley. 

A joyful signature that concludes with a powerful, structured base of woody notes blended with enveloping White Musks. 

A fresh and vibrant trail that retains a radiant force.

Name: dune - eau de toilette
Description: An oceanic fragrance, created in harmony with nature, this radiant, fresh and subtle accord captures the landscape where the sky meets the sea in a warm, oceanic floral bouquet. Enveloping, serene and sensual.

Name: dior addict - eau de parfum
Description:
Dior Addict Eau de Parfum unleashes fresh and captivating top notes that blend Mandarin Leaf with Tunisian Orange Blossom. 

Intense and vibrant, it reveals a powerful heart of Jasmine Sambac Absolute that blossoms with soft femininity and sensuality. The base unfurls in the deep and exquisite warmth of Bourbon Vanilla. 

A soft and seductive trail tinged with light.

Name: poison girl - iridescent beautifying body milk
Description: A Poison Girl essential. It moisturizes   and enhances the skin's radiance with a subtle shimmer effect. Generously scented, the Body Milk prolongs and intensifies the scent of Poison Girl.

Name: poison girl - unexpected roller-pearl
Description:
Experience Poison Girl Unexpected in the new Roller-Pearl. A discreetly elegant bottle, topped with a delicate pearl to create an entirely new way to apply fragrance. A new gesture that is simple, sensual, and liberating. 

For fragrance touch-ups or perfuming on the go, Poison Girl Unexpected Roller-Pearl is as precious as a gem. 


PRECISE, CONTROLLED APPLICATION: The glass bead tip delivers just the right amount of fragrance, right where desired, with no waste.

VELVET TOUCH: The texture is luxuriously sensual, ultra-light, and fresh. 

TRAVEL: The 20 ml bottle goes anywhere. It is hermetically sealed with a screw-on cap.


With Poison Girl Unexpected, François Demachy, Dior Perfumer-Creator, shakes up refined ingredients with sassy, spirited accords to create a new fresh and sparkling floral that is entirely Unexpected!


The new Roller-Peral is perfect for a Poison Girl who wants to apply her fragrance with confidence, whenever, wherever.

Name: pure poison - y0083201
Description: Once upon a time, there was a fragrance that was innocent yet captivating, sincere yet mysterious… Pure Poison incarnates seduction in its purest state by exploring its duality and irresistible alchemy. Based on orange blossom, jasmine, gardenia, amber and sandalwood, this delicate yet generous modern potion reveals the seductress within.

Name: hypnotic poison - eau de toilette
Description:
The mystery of Dior’s legendary forbidden fruit lives on in a magical, modern potion that blends femininity with boldness. 

Four contrasting facets 

– intoxicating bitter almond and caraway spice, opulent Sambac jasmine, mysterious Jacarandra and sensuous vanilla and musk

– make for a compelling, bewitching fragrance fusion. Intoxicating and extravagant.

Name: poison girl - roller-pearl eau de toilette
Description:
Experience Poison Girl Eau de Toilette in the new Roller-Pearl. A discreetly elegant bottle, topped with a delicate pearl to create an entirely new way to apply fragrance. A new gesture that is simple, sensual, and liberating. 

For fragrance touch-ups or perfuming on the go, Poison Girl Eau de Toilette Roller-Pearl is as precious as a gem. 


PRECISE, CONTROLLED APPLICATION: The glass bead tip delivers just the right amount of fragrance, right where desired, with no waste.

VELVET TOUCH: The texture is luxuriously sensual, ultra-light, and fresh. 

TRAVEL: The 20 ml bottle goes anywhere. It is hermetically sealed with a screw-on cap.


Poison Girl Eau de Toilette is a composition with a distinctive beat. 

An appeal to the senses in three movements that plays with a daring encounter between contrasting ingredients. 

A duo of frosted orange engaged in a juicy dialogue. Non-identical twins with complementary characters. Followed by a bouquet of sensual flowers, creating a fiery climate of hot and cold.

Ever-present in the sensual and addictive signature of Poison Girl, notes of tonka bean and vanilla distill their racy, bitter-sweet caress.

Name: poison girl - eau de toilette
Description: Poison Girl is a floral gourmand that seduces with a fruity floral top note and the addictive base. Its appeal to the senses plays on a bold blend between contrasting raw materials. A pairing of icy-cool and juicy oranges complement each other while armfuls of sensual flowers introduce a spirited hot & cold ambiance. Lastly, Tonka Bean and Vanilla notes spread their sensual and bittersweet caress. This Poison Girl breaks the ice, mastering the allure she has.

Name: poison - eau de toilette
Description: Some perfumes are born a myth. Provocative and mysterious since its creation, Poison is Dior’s ultimate weapon of seduction. Its exceptional alchemy is created by a rich blend of spicy, fruity and amber notes with sensual honey and musk accords. An unforgettable and charismatic oriental fragrance.

Name: poison girl - eau de parfum
Description: Poison Girl is the fragrance of a modern girl, free and sexy. A delicious lure, poisoning instantly then drawing out its pleasures to the point of addiction. Poison Girl makes a direct statement, ravishing and addictive. An immediate, in-your-face effect.

Name: poison - extrait de parfum
Description: Poison is a skin scent like no other. In the Extrait de Parfum, François Demachy revisited the legendary accord by enhancing its sensual character. Highlighting the strength of its spicy notes, he created a floral elixir with a deep, lingering trail of scent. With raw materials like Coriander, Vanilla, Tuberose Absolute and Rose de Mai Absolute. The Poison bottle was designed like forbidden fruit sculpted in an amethyst with deep reflections of light. Gold thread tied by hand around its neck adds another precious touch. Each bottle is sealed with a baudruche film, adorned with a perfumer bow, and affixed with the Dior wax stamp.

Name: miss dior - nourishing rose hand cream
Description: This rich cream gently nourishes the hands. Its formula enriched with soothing Centifolia rose water moisturizes the skin and penetrates quickly, for beautiful, protected and delicately scented hands.

Name: miss dior - perfumed deodorant
Description: This perfumed deodorant offers protection and freshness all day long.     Its gentle formula, enriched with rose extract, provides lasting protection for the skin.     Your skin is refreshed with a delicate scent as the trail of your Miss Dior fragrance is intensified.

Name: miss dior - silky soap
Description: This silky soap gently cleanses the skin. Its fresh, creamy lather leaves a delicate fragrance. The emblematic hounds tooth pattern provides an elegant touch.

Name: miss dior - foaming shower gel
Description:
This scented foaming shower gel produces a generous lather that gently cleanses the skin. Its fresh formula, enriched with rose oil, which is known for its nourishing properties, brings beauty and comfort to the skin. 

Your skin is enhanced with a delicate scent as the trail of your Miss Dior fragrance is intensified.

Name: miss dior - silky body mist
Description: Airy and sensual, Miss Dior Silky Body Mist delicately perfumes and beautifies the skin. Its easy to apply formula combines the benefits of an enhancing body care with the freshness of a mist. This light and non-oily body mist softens and preserves the skin's hydration for up to 6 hours. Create your intensified custom scent by applying either alone or layered underneath any Miss Dior fragrance.

Name: miss dior - fresh body creme
Description:
This perfume body creme melts delicately into the skin to provide comfort and softness. Its fresh and creamy texture enriched with rose oil moisturizes and nourishes the skin without leaving a greasy film. 

Generously scented, your skin is suppler and the trail of your Miss Dior fragrance is intensified.

Name: miss dior - hair mist
Description:
Perfuming your hair is a gesture as delicate as it is evocative. It dates back to the dawn of time, the indication of a mysterious femininity. Miss Dior proposes a new perfumed hair mist that sculpts a seductive elegance. 

Miss Dior Hair Mist possesses true intensity, while keeping hair fresh. Enriched with active ingredients, its formula literally dresses the hair in a sensual trail.

Name: miss dior - fresh rose body oil
Description: This dual-action rose oil tones and nourishes skin and hair. Shake the bottle to activate the two phases: Centifolia rose water adds a light, fresh quality to the dry oil for a satiny finish with no oily residue. It protects skin and hair while intensifying the scent of Miss Dior fragrance.

Name: miss dior - moisturizing body milk
Description:
This moisturizing body milk hydrates and enhances the skin on a daily basis. Its light and fresh texture enriched with Centifolia Rose extract penetrates quickly to nourish, moisturize and leave skin felling soft. 

Subtly scented, your skin is suppler and the trail of your Miss Dior fragrance is intensified.

Name: miss dior - eau de toilette originale
Description: Miss Dior Original is the very first fragrance by Christian Dior. Its avant-garde green chypre floral accord revolutionized perfume and embodies the perfection of the couturier’s mark. L'Eau de Toilette Originale more gently deploys this bold trail, which has become a great classic. The extreme refinement of the Galbanum notes brings ultimate freshness to its floral heart of Jasmine and Grasse Rose Absolute, while Patchouli Essence gives the fragrance its impertinence.

Name: miss dior original - extrait de parfum
Description: Miss Dior Original is the very first fragrance by Christian Dior. Its avant-garde green chypre floral accord revolutionized perfume and embodies the perfection of the couturier’s mark. L'Extrait de Parfum Original intensely deploys this bold trail, which has become a great classic. The extreme refinement of the galbanum notes brings ultimate freshness to its floral heart of jasmine and Grasse rose absolute, while patchouli essence gives the fragrance its impertinence. Its precious bottle is cut like a suit and decorated with the iconic hounds tooth motif. Sealed by hand using the baudruchage technique, the bottle is adorned with a silver thread and grey satin couture bow carved into a swallow tail. Minimalist and modern, the result is bold and extremely elegant.

Name: miss dior  - blooming bouquet
Description: The fresh and sparkling Miss Dior Blooming Bouquet is a composition designed like a dress embroidered with a thousand flowers. This floral bouquet pays homage to Christian Dior’s legendary passion for flowers. Its heart holds a tender accord of Peony and Damascus Rose refreshed by a radiant Calabrian Bergamot. The poetic trail is enveloped in soft notes of White Musk. A floral springtime creation for a playful and charming Miss Dior.

Name: dior grand bal plume et nacre ø 33 mm, automatic movement, "dior inversé 8 1/4" calibre
Description: The Dior Grand Bal collection swirls like a ball gown to the rhythm of the “Dior inversé” calibre and functional oscillating weight placed on top of the dial which drive the timepiece. Resulting from strict aesthetic requirements, this watch complication echoes Monsieur Dior’s designs. “The ball gown makes you dream and must make you a dream woman.” Like satin, faille and taffeta constructed into opulent and architectural party dresses in the Maison’s ateliers, the Dior Grand Bal is adorned in gold threads, net, silk, feathers, gems or scarab beetle elytra. Sure of their attractions, these refined materials and their whirlwind of colours invite us to take the floor and twirl around all night long.

For fragrance touch-ups or perfuming on the go, Miss Dior Blooming Bouquet Roller-Pearl is as precious as a gem.

VELVET TOUCH: The texture is luxuriously sensual, ultra-light, and fresh.

Name: dior grand bal pièce unique galaxie andromeda Ø 36 mm, automatic movement, "dior inversé 11 1/2" caliber
Description: "A ball gown must be the one of your dreams, and must also make you a dream-like creature," said Christian Dior. This is why the Dior Grand Bal collection is reminiscent of the swirling of a ball gown, in time with the "Dial Inversé" caliber and its functional oscillating weight on the front of the dial. Just like the structured satin, faille and taffeta fabrics that grace the sumptuous party dresses in Dior's couture workshops, the Dior Grand Bal collection boasts golden threads, mesh, silk, feathers and stones as well as beetle wings. Technical watchmaking innovation is now at the service of femininity. Refined materials and a kaleidoscope of colors evoke the magical balls that were so dear to Monsieur Dior, inviting the wearer to glide onto the dance floor.

Description: Malachite dial, faceted hour and minute hands.

Name: dior grand bal miss dior  Ø 36mm, automatic movement, “dior inversé 11 1/2” calibre
Description: The Dior Grand Bal collection swirls like a ball gown to the rhythm of the “Dior Inversé” calibre and functional oscillating weight placed on top of the dial which drive the timepiece. Resulting from strict aesthetic requirements, this watch complication echoes Monsieur Dior’s designs. “The ball gown makes you dream and must make you a dream woman.” Like satin, faille and taffeta constructed into opulent and architectural party dresses in the Maison’s ateliers, the Dior Grand Bal is adorned in gold threads, net, silk, feathers, gems or scarab beetle elytra. Sure of their attractions, these refined materials and their whirlwind of colours invite us to take the floor and twirl around all night long.

Name: dior grand bal plume noire  Ø 36mm, automatic movement, “dior inversé 11 1/2” calibre
Description: Black sun-brushed dial decorated with yellow gold threads, faceted hour and minute hands.

Name: dior grand bal fête du printemps ø 36mm, automatic movement, “dior inversé 11 1/2” calibre
Description: White mother-of-pearl dial set with diamonds and rubies, faceted hour and minute hands.

Name: miss dior - absolutely blooming roller-pearl
Description:
Be surrounded in Miss Dior Absolutely Blooming in the new Roller-Pearl. A discreetly elegant glass bottle, topped with a delicate pearl for a free and easy new approach to fragrance application. 

For fragrance touch-ups or perfuming on the go, Miss Dior Absolutely Blooming Roller-Pearl is as precious as a gem.


PRECISE, CONTROLLED APPLICATION: The glass bead tip delivers just the right amount of fragrance, right where desired, with no waste.

VELVET TOUCH: The texture is luxuriously sensual, ultra-light, and fresh.

TRAVEL: The 20 ml bottle goes anywhere. It is hermetically sealed with a screw-on cap.

Bright and colorful, Miss Dior Absolutely Blooming is an extravagant floral delight you return to again and again. Its top notes captivate with a joyful, tangy burst of red berries. At the heart, a sublime duo of Grasse and Damascus roses embraces a sensual peony accord. This infinite blooming of fresh flowers is comforted in a base of white musk notes.

Name: miss dior - absolutely blooming
Description: Bright and colorful, Miss Dior Absolutely Blooming is a floral delight you return to over and over. Its top notes of tangy Red Berry are joyful and striking. At its heart, a sublime duet of Grass and Damascan Roses embraces a sensuous Peony accord. This infinite blooming of fresh flowers is comforted in a base of White Musk notes. A positive and joyful harmony for a playful and irresistible Miss Dior.

Name: miss dior - eau de toilette
Description: The enticing and radiant Miss Dior Eau de Toilette embodies the delicateness of a luminous chypre floral. Sparkling blood orange brightens the essences of Tunisian neroli and Damascus rose. A luminous composition underscored by Indonesian patchouli, giving the fragrance its personality.

Name: miss dior - eau de parfum
Description: The new Miss Dior Eau de Parfum reveals the femininity of a sensual floral. Its heart is a floral declaration that combines the beauty of Grasse rose with the boldness of Damascus rose, both wrapped in a ribbon of fresh Calabrian bergamot. This handcrafted creation is woven with rosewood from French Guiana and pink pepper from Réunion Island for heightened character. A Miss Dior that will leave you lovestruck.

Name: miss dior - absolutely blooming signature set
Description:
Discover your perfume with its 

travel spray and miniature in an exclusive couture Christmas gift wrap:

- Eau de Parfum Spray 100ml

- Eau de Parfum Refillable Travel Spray 10 ml

- Eau de Parfum Miniature 5 ml

Name: miss dior - le parfum
Description:
Voluptuous and captivating, Miss Dior Le Parfum is the quintessence of an exceptional Oriental floral fragrance.

Its heart of Grasse rose absolute is enveloped in an Indonesian patchouli essence that smolders upon contact with a Tunisian orange blossom absolute. Its remarkable lingering scent is tinged with a touch of fresh Sicilian mandarin and warm vanilla notes that reveal the enchanting femininity of this exceptional fragrance.

Name: skull necklace, 18k white gold, diamonds and blue chalcedony
Description: A memento mori that’s joyful and festive: through these creations, Victoire de Castellane reminds us to make the most of the present.

Name: miss dior - signature set
Description:

- Miss Dior 5ml miniature

Name: miss dior - signature set
Description:
Discover your perfume with its moisturizing body milk in an exclusive couture Christmas gift wrap:                                                                                           

- Eau de Parfum Spray 50 ml 

- Moisturizing Body Milk 75ml

Name: miss dior - eau de parfum
Description:
Discover Miss Dior Eau de Parfum 100ml in an exclusive couture Christmas gift wrap.


The Miss Dior Eau de Parfum reveals the femininity of a sensual floral. Its heart is a floral declaration that combines the beauty of Grasse rose with the boldness of Damascus rose, both wrapped in a ribbon of fresh Calabrian bergamot. This handcrafted creation is woven with rosewood from French Guiana and pink pepper from Réunion Island for heightened character. A Miss Dior that will leave you lovestruck.

Name: miss dior - blooming bouquet
Description:
Discover Miss Dior Blooming Bouquet Eau de Toilette 100ml in an exclusive couture Christmas gift wrap.


Miss Dior Blooming Bouquet is a fresh, vivacious composition designed like a dress embroidered with a thousand blossoms. This floral bouquet pays tribute to Christian Dior's legendary love for flowers. At its heart is the tenderness of a peony and Damascus rose accord tailored by radiant Calabrian bergamot. Its poetic, lingering scent is edged with white musk lace. A floral springtime signature for a joyful, charming Miss Dior.

Name: j'adore - silky soap
Description:
This silky soap boasts the protective and nourishing properties of Cotton nectar*. Enriched with Ylang Ylang essential oil, it offers a feeling of freshness and well-being while maintaining the skin's natural balance.


* In vitro test.

Name: j'adore - dry silky body oil
Description: Incredibly sensual and sophisticated, this dry silky body oil is an ode to flowers that extends the sensory pleasure of J'adore. Enriched with the hydrating and relaxing properties of Ylang Ylang essential oil, the dry oil soothes and moisturizes as it enhances the skin tone. Its luxurious texture absorbs quickly, leaving the skin soft to the touch. The powerful notes of this unique oil bring new fullness and leave an intense fragrance trail that blends beautifully with the scent of J’adore. An oil as intricate as an elixir, housed in an iconic amphora bottle.

Name: j'adore - huile divine
Description: The Rose de Grasse makes its debut in the J'adore bath collection. Created by Dior Perfumer-Creator, François Demachy, Huile Divine is an invitation to enjoy two different, highly sensorial moments - in the bath or on the skin. Add a few drops of Huile Divine to your bath and indulge in a milky soak that sensually envelops the body. As the inimitable accords of the J'adore floral bouquet are released, the bath is transformed into a relaxing treatment, and its nourishing properties soften the skin. For another irresistible experience, simply apply Huile Divine directly onto the skin. It glides on lightly, is easily absorbed, hydrates and provides a sensation of softness. Your skin is radiant, nourished and scented.

Name: j'adore - beautifying body creme
Description: This intensely smooth beautifying creme is enriched with cotton nectar and pansy flower extracts to nourish and moisturize the skin throughout the day. Enriched with ultra-fine pearlescent pigments, it leaves the skin instantly supple and radiant. Its generous fragrance recreates all the intensity of the J'adore floral bouquet.

Name: j'adore - body mist
Description:
Airy and sensual, this precious mist envelops the body in a delicate, refreshing cloud of scent and maintains the skin's moisturization.

A formula for more beautiful and instantly soft skin. A new, irresistible way to enhance your skin and bathe it in the scent of J'adore.

Name: j'adore - hair mist
Description: A generous and feminine gesture. The effect is light and leaves a subtle trail. In its travel-friendly amphora, J’adore Hair Mist is a new hair fragrance that you can take everywhere. In a single step, it illuminates the hair and enhances it with the fresh and floral trail of J’adore: Juicy and sparkling Blood Orange, the green burst of Neroli from Grasse, the sensually spirited Damascus Rose.

Name: j'adore - rich shower gel
Description: The rich shower gel provides the protective and nourishing properties of Cotton nectar*. Its creamy texture is enhanced with Ylang Ylang essential oil, renowned for its relaxing properties, to deliver a feeling of well-being and leave the skin soft while maintaining its natural balance.*In vitro test.

Name: j’adore - beautifying body milk
Description:
This light emulsion has a gentle, milky texture enriched with Cotton nectar and Jasmin flower extract to moisturize* and enhance the skin. Delicately fragranced, the beautifying body milk subtly recreates the trail of J'adore.

* Moisturizes the upper layers of the skin.

Name: j'adore - extrait de parfum
Description:
J’adore is the fragrance of flowers that bloom with absolute femininity. For the Extrait de Parfum, François Demachy wanted to give dense and dazzling expression to the primary accord. Seeking an extreme concentration, he composed a generous and intense bouquet of flowers that work in a beautiful harmony. Using ingredients with character like Rose de Mai Absolute, Damascus Rose Absolute, Jasmine Sambac Absolute and Ylang-Ylang Essence. 


The J’adore bottle is a modern expression of the amphora Christian Dior chose for his first olfactory creations. Made entirely of glass, each bottle is hand-gilded with fine gold, sealed with a baudruche film, tightly wrapped with gold thread, and affixed with the Dior seal.

Name: j'adore - touche de parfum
Description: J’adore explores every woman’s ultimate fantasy: to create her own personalized scent tailored for each unique moment and desire. Touche de Parfum is a new olfactory and sensory experience created by Dior Perfumer-Creator François Demachy, using only the finest raw materials. Either on its own or with a corresponding J’adore fragrance, choose the number of drops of Touche de Parfum according to the desired level of intensity. The sensual texture of Touche de Parfum will mix with the chosen J’adore fragrance to create an exclusive, seductive signature scent.

Name: j'adore - l'or
Description:
Sublime, sensual, J’adore L’Or is the quintessence of the J'adore floral bouquet, combining jasmine and May rose absolutes, grown at our exclusive estates in Grasse, with the oriental charm of vanilla and tuberose. Jasmine grandiflorum shines with intense, enveloping floral power and fruity accents. The May rose reveals its sensuous strength and immediate beauty with touches of spice. Intermingled with these two absolutes, vanilla entices and embraces while keeping its slightly raucous charm, and tuberose — a vision of beauty in white — mesmerizes with its relentless fervor.


The sensorial intensity is now adorned with a new chiseled necklace, created using a unique engraving technique. As precious as the most beautiful of jewels worn on the skin, J’adore L’Or comes to life, sensual and carnal like the liquid gold that flows through it.

Name: j'adore - eau de toilette
Description:
François Demachy, Dior Perfumer-Creator, wanted to accentuate the luminous character of J’adore eau Lumiere eau de Toilette, highlighting its contrasts, fine-tuning its facets, and renewing its freshness while staying true to its floral signature. A desire to fill it with even more light, joy and zest for life. 

Joyful top notes explode and captivate, as Essence of Blood Orange awakens the senses and wets the appetite. The sweetness of Magnolia tinged with vanilla and lemon meets the quivering and lively beauty of Damascus Rose. The Essences unfurl, drawing with them Neroli from Vallauris chosen above all others for its unique accents. As radiant as the white of its petals, as warm as the golden Mediterranean sun. An intense flower that casts its light and lets J’adore shine.

Name: j'adore - in joy
Description:
J'adore in joy is a perfume that literally ""smells"" of joy. A new, instant pleasure, an exclamation that springs forth like a declaration of love for life: J'adore in joy! 


François Demachy, Dior Perfumer-Creator, has created a salty treat that is both original and surprising… 

A flower with a freshness that is full and lively, soft and incisive, custom-crafted in Grasse. 

J’adore in joy has a charm like no other that seizes the senses with a daring floral-fruity-salty accord. Ylang-Ylang Essence from Madagascar and Jasmine Sambac are brightened with a refreshing Fleur de Sel note and bursting with juicy Peach. A light and salty nectar, as refreshing as a beautiful, ripe fruit.

Name: j'adore - eau de parfum
Description: J’adore eau de parfum is the great women's floral fragrance by Dior. A bouquet finely crafted down to the last detail, like a custom-made flower. Essence of ylang-ylang with its floral-fruity notes and essence of Damascus Rose from Turkey blend with a rare duo of Jasmine Grandiflorum from Grasse and Indian Sambac Jasmine with fruity and voluptuous sensuality.

Name: j'adore - absolu
Description:
J'adore absolu is the new floral nectar by the House of Dior. In an incredibly lush composition, François Demachy blends voluptuous and sensual floral absolutes. Absolutes of Grasse Jasmine, Sambac Jasmine, Rose and Magnolia intertwine with unprecedented freshness: flowers take on the sweetness of a delicious syrup, a sublime, natural and seductive nectar.

J'adore absolu is built around Grasse Jasmine, a capricious beauty that requires patience, harvested at the precise moment when, drenched in sunlight, it releases its most sensual accents.

Name: j'adore - signature set
Description:
Discover your fragrance with its beautifying body milk in an exclusive couture Christmas gift wrap:

- Eau de Parfum Spray 50 ml

- Beautifying Body Milk 75 ml

Name: 30 montaigne coffret - montaigne
Category: Fragrance/Women's Fragrance/Les Créations de Monsieur Dior
Description:
Let yourself be captivated by this collection of five iconic fragrances. In this exclusive coffret decorated with the illustrious Dior façade, you'll find five enchantments for the senses. 


Miss Dior Blooming Bouquet Eau de Toilette (7.5 ml), the delicateness of a fresh Rose dressed in Peony. 

Poison Girl Eau de Toilette (5 ml), a vibrant, hot-cold, ultra-sensual floral. 

J'adore Eau de Parfum (5ml), the intensity of a unique, radiant floral bouquet enhanced by Grasse Jasmine. 

Diorissimo Eau de Toilette (7.5 ml), a fragrance that enhances the freshness of Lily-of-the-Valley, Monsieur Dior's lucky-charm flower. 

Forever & Ever Eau de Toilette (7.5 ml), a fresh, tender, delicate Rose.

Name: j'adore - signature set
Description:
Discover your fragrance along with a travel spray in an exclusive couture Christmas gift wrap:

- Eau de Parfum Spray 100 ml 

- Eau de Parfum Refillable Travel Spray 10 ml

Name: j'adore - eau de parfum
Description:
Discover J 'adore Eau de Parfum 100 ml in an exlcusive couture Christmas gift wrap.


J'adore Eau de Parfum is the ideal bouquet,  finely crafted down to the last detail, like a custom-made flower. Essence of Ylang-Ylang from the Comoros unfurls its floral-fruity notes and instills a soft exotic touch. Damascus Rose, sophisticated and exuberant, then comes to warm the senses. Last but not least, a duo of Jasmines echo one another in a perfect embrace. Jasmine Grandiflorum from Grasse, the quintessence of a noble floral, exudes its delicate sensuality, tinged with fruit and sun. It works in harmony with the more carnal quality of Indian Jasmine Sambac, ""flower of the gods,"" with its warm facets of incredibly sensual, enveloping orange blossom.

Name: j'adore - eau de toilette
Description:
Discover J 'adore Injoy Eau de Toilette 100 ml in an exclusive couture Christmas gift wrap.


J'adore Injoy is a perfume that literally ""smells"" of joy. A new, instant pleasure, an exclamation that springs forth like a declaration of love for life: J'adore Injoy!


François Demachy, Dior Perfumer-Creator, has created a salted sensation that is both original and surprising. A flower with a freshness that is full and lively, soft and incisive, custom-crafted in Grasse.

J’adore Injoy has a charm like no other that seizes the senses with a daring floral-fruity-salty accord. Ylang-ylang essence from Madagascar and jasmine sambac are brightened with a refreshing fleur de sel note and bursting with juicy peach. A light and salty nectar, as refreshing as a beautiful, ripe fruit.

Name: joy by dior - moisturizing body lotion
Description:
JOY by Dior Moisturizing Body Lotion is a body care product that enhances and nourishes the skin day after day. Its fresh and airy texture helps ensure rapid absorption. 

Like a caress, this creamy body milk envelops you in a sensation of well-being and intensifies the fragrance trail.

Name: dior addict lacquer plump - lip plumping lacquered ink, long-wear colour
Description: The first plumping lacquered ink by Dior that provides long-wear color,  intense lacquered shine, and an incredibly comfortable texture.

Name: dior addict lip maximizer - lip plumper
Category: Makeup/Look & Exclusives/Summer Look 2018 - Cool Wave/Cool Summer
Description: The 1st instant-volume lip gloss from backstage at Dior.

Name: diorific lipstick - limited edition - velvet colour lipstick - weightless, long-wearing
Category: Makeup/Look & Exclusives/MIDNIGHT WISH - HOLIDAY LOOK 2018/FAIRYTALE KISSES
Description: Diorific, the legendary accessory with an Haute Couture finish, the signature of Dior glamour housed in a golden ""jewel"" case.

Name: diorific - haute couture long wearing lipstick
Description: Diorific, the legendary lip accessory with an Haute Couture finish, holds the signature of Dior glamour in its jewel-like gold case.

Name: diorific khôl - christmas 2017 limited edition - powder lipstick – ultra-pigmented – long-wear intensity
Description:
For the first time ever, Diorific is now available as a kohl for lips. Delivers intense color with a powdery, matte finish.


Simply irresistible. Pure glamour. The faceted bullet makes applying lipstick almost magical.

Name: dior addict lacquer stick - liquified shine, saturated lip colour, weightless wear
Description:
Dior brings you the next generation of lipstick: a full coverage lacquer lipstick delivering high shine and intense color with just one swipe.  The high-pigment pop shades glide on easily with one-coat coverage. Enjoy weightless, comfortable wear for hours. 


""For this new generation of lacquers, I wanted the comfort of a hydrating balm without compromising on color intensity and shine. All this beauty can be found in one stick: our Dior Addict Lacquer Stick.""

Peter Philips, Creative and Image Director for Dior Makeup

Name: dior addict
Description:
Dior ushers in a new era in lip makeup with the breakthrough creation of a lipstick that boasts a hydra-gel core with a top coat effect for sensational mirror shine. 

Concentrated in the shape of a CD at the center, the ultra-moisturizing soft core runs the full length of the stick. Application after application, it works like a top coat, adding an extra dose of shine and colourfastness with unbelievable comfort.

Name: dior addict lipstick - limited edition - hydra-gel core mirror shine
Description:
Dior ushers in a new era in lip makeup with the breakthrough creation of a lipstick that boasts a hydra-gel core with a top coat effect for sensational mirror shine.


Concentrated in the shape of a CD at the center, the ultra-moisturizing soft core runs the full length of the stick. Application after application, it works like a top coat, adding an extra dose of shine and colourfastness with unbelievable comfort.

Name: dior addict lipstick - limited edition - y0028760
Category: Makeup/Look & Exclusives/Summer Look 2018 - Cool Wave/Cool Summer
Description: Dior ushers in a new era in lip makeup with the breakthrough creation of a lipstick that boasts a hydra-gel core with a top coat effect for sensational mirror shine.

Name: rouge dior bijou - limited edition - jewel lipstick - couture colour - comfort & wear
Category: Makeup/Look & Exclusives/MIDNIGHT WISH - HOLIDAY LOOK 2018/MAKE A WISH
Description: To celebrate the season, Rouge Dior has been released in a festive collector's edition featuring a band set with stars and a stick engraved with a wish: “Love”, “Faith”, Luck”, “Bliss” and “Thrill"".

Name: dior addict lipstick - y0028751
Description:
Dior ushers in a new era in lip makeup with the breakthrough creation of a lipstick that boasts a hydra-gel core with a top coat effect for sensational mirror shine.

Concentrated in the shape of a CD at the center, the ultra-moisturizing soft core runs the full length of the stick. Application after application, it works like a top coat, adding an extra dose of shine and lasting colour with unbelievable comfort.

Name: rouge dior
Description: A selection of four Rouge Dior miniatures in a wide range of colors with matte or satiny finishes. From vibrant red to romantic rosewood and irresistible plum, lips take on a variety of shades to suit any beauty look.

Name: rouge dior liquid - limited edition - liquid lip stain. intense couture colour. extreme long-wear. 3 effects: matte, metal, satin
Description:
Rouge Dior has yet again been reinvented with the first liquid lipstick formula by Dior with multiple effects and surprising colour impact. Coverage, 12h* long wear and comfort: a true gem available in 3 vibrant finishes – matte, metal and satin.


* Instrumental test carried out on 20 subjects.

Name: rouge dior liquid - liquid lip stain. intense couture colour. extreme long-wear. 3 effects: matte, metal, satin
Description:
Now Rouge Dior has been reinvented as the first liquid lipstick formula by Dior with multiple effects and surprising color impact. Rouge Liquid saturates lips with comfort and coverage, delivering 12-hour* long wear. Available in 3 vibrant finishes: Matte, Metal and Satin.


*Clinical test, 20 women

Name: rouge dior double rouge - matte metal colour & couture contour lipstick
Description:
Inspired by professional makeup artistry, Double Rouge combines two makeup trends: matte and metal. 


In a single application, it produces an ombré effect with a highly pigmented matte contour and a light-catching metal heart.

Name: rouge dior - spring look 2018 limited edition - couture colour lipstick - comfort & wear
Category: Makeup/Look & Exclusives/Glow Addict Collection - Spring Look 2018/AWAKEN THE SMILE
Description: The iconic Rouge Dior celebrates the season with ultra-feminine, springtime hues.

Name: rouge dior ultra rouge - ultra pigmented hydra lipstick - 12h** weightless wear
Description:
Rouge Dior Ultra Rouge is the first incredibly long-wearing lipstick with the comfort of a lip ink*: a true revolution in the history of lipstick. Ultra Rouge offers a lightweight, ultra-comfortable formula and all the colour of a high-pigmentation lipstick. The colours seem more saturated with a luminous, semi-matte finish** for incredible sensoriality and hydration. 

* At Dior. 

** Instrumental test carried out on 20 subjects. Except shade 000.

Name: double rouge lolli'glow - limited edition - matte metal colour & couture contour lipstick
Description: This spring, Double Rouge lipstick by Dior plays on the contrast between a vibrant hue and a pastel shade: its creamy texture colours the lips like candy.

Name: rouge dior - limited edition - couture colour lipsticks - comfort & wear
Category: Makeup/Look & Exclusives/DIOR EN DIABLE - FALL LOOK 2018/Obscure object of desire
Description:
With Rouge Dior and its cult formula of 16-hour* comfort, women feel good, no matter the colour, no matter the finish --satin or matte.


Rediscover the iconic Rouge Dior with the six new bewitching shades revealed in the Rouge en Diable collection. The revered formula remains unchanged. Lips are dressed in joyfully devilish shades that harmonize perfectly with the eyes and nails.


A true object of desire, Rough Dior comes in a new metallic couture case with an elegant clasp. The interior of each cap bears the Rouge 999 shade, Dior's flamboyantly sexy signature. 



* Auto-scoring by 60 women.

Name: rouge dior - y0027830
Description:
With Rouge Dior and its cult formula of 16h* comfort, women feel good, no matter the color no matter the finish satin or matte. A palette of colors with iconic reds, vibrant corals, passionate pink, romantic rosewoods and extreme and surprising matte shades. A true object of desire, Rouge Dior comes with a new metallic couture case crafted with discreet details : for a touch of personal luxury, the inside of each cap is attired in the Rouge 999 shade, Dior's flamboyantly sexy signature.


*Auto-scorage on 60 women

Name: dior universal contour - universal contour lipliner
Description:
The universal lip liner from Dior Backstage.

Dior Contour Universel is a totally transparent lip liner that suits all skin tones and all shades of lipstick. It smoothes and lines lips for a clean, precise lip contour and lasting hold.

*Test in use - 32 women

Name: dior backstage lip palette - multi-finish, concentrated colors prime, plump, color, contour
Description:
The Dior Backstage Lip Palette is the Dior makeup artists' secret weapon to create an array of pro lip looks from ultra-natural to bold. 

A collection of makeup artist essentials inspired by the energy backstage at the runway shows, this palette offers shades that adapt to any skin tone, in buildable matte, satin and glossy finishes.

Name: dior addict lip maximizer - maximum hydration & volume effect instant & long-term
Description: Dior Addict Lip Maximizer, now a must-have for makeup artists, is the 1st Dior backstage lip plumping gloss for smooth, hydrated lips and an instant, long-lasting plump effect.

Name: lip sugar scrub - self-vanishing sweet exfoliating lip balm - color awakening
Description: All makeup artists know that healthy, moisturized lips are the key to optimal color impact. The latest from Backstage Pros: A Lip Sugar Scrub - an exfoliating and nourishing stick with grains of sugar that melt away, for incredibly softer lips and a naturally rosy finish.

Name:
lip sugar scrub - 
limited edition - self-vanishing sweet exfoliating lip balm - color awakening
Description: This spring, Dior Addict Lip Sugar Scrub cares for our lips with a delicious texture in a raspberry pink shade.

Name: dior addict lip glow to the max - double color & glow awakening - hydrating lip balm
Description: Dior Addict Lip Glow To The Max: the 1st Dior backstage lip balm with ""Color & Glow"" action that naturally revives color for fresh, outrageously radiant lips.
